data.description: Nicely updated 2BR 2 BA main house + 1BR 300 sq ft cabana on paved road on half acre, no HOA, new roof 2022, repiped 2023, AC 2022, no carpet, fenced yard. The kitchen is nicely updated with granite counters and stainless appliances and you will enjoy having both a living and family room, plus plenty of storage space and a wonderful master bedroom suite, plus a utility room, and just a lot of space to spread out in this sweet home on a nice street in our beautiful town, make it yours! Cash or conventional financing only, no FHA or VA. Sold AS IS with right to inspect.
